Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:35.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back Sanji
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who was being pressed into a marriage\Nand left his friends behind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others infiltrated the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:44.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Whole Cake Island\Nwhere Emperor Big Mom is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brook who snuck into the Whole Cake Chateau
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:51.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to get a copy of the Road Ponegliff,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}faced Big Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Sanji, determined\Nto marry Pudding,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}came to know her true colors\Nand deadly plan for the wedding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop dreaming!\NWill I marry that lowlife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was trying to set us up\Nfrom the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Sanji ever do to her?!\NDammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama's aim was to get your \NArmy of Clone Soldiers and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,scientific technology from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the wedding tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you Vinsmokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will all be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Undaunted Soul!\NBrook vs. Big Mom!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so unfortunate to have\Nsuch a dumb brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It seems like she's gonna pass out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's been bleeding a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave her like this, she'll \Nbe dead before the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd save us the trouble,\Nwouldn't it, Pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let that happen.\NThat'll ruin our whole plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need her to live until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can eliminate all of you Vinsmokes\Nfrom this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Big Sister-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll give us trouble if you die like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll give us trouble\Nif you reveal my ungraceful nature
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you've just seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm. It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of the Memo-Memo Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has a roll of film in their minds\Nthat records memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have scary experiences and sad memories
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and things that you wanna forget, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Come to my room and lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed with Germa 66.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd been shot in the leg but \Nyou still made it that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're uselessly tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I paste strips of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from some soldier who's been shot \Nby a stray bullet here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Edit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your most recent memories \Ninvolving me have been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a joyous wedding tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the soldiers and\Ntake her to the medical center.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:16.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,TREASURE REPOSITORY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is he for real?\N--Are you really gonna fight Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I need a copy of that stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But let's do it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gavotte Bond en Avant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't so much as lay a finger on Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lesson I'll be sure you learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swallow Bond en Avant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul King. Do you wanna stop \Nfighting and surrender now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.\NI still have an ace up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know their weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the Chess Peacekeepers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you three are infused with someone \Nelse's souls through Big Mom's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Soul King will rest those souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How come? Why is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also a good guitar player.\NI want you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear what she said?\NJust come here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll be back right after this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! That was too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, Mama, he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, you went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be added to my precious collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:14:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Can't you control your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more merciless than them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You can still move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mama, leave him to me.\N--No, to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do it!\NI'll give him the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't kill him!\NI can handle it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first! Then you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's not fair!\N--Shut up! Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No.\N--Do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?\NThat's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Napoleon, you can't cut in!\N--That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it because you guys were too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally quieted down, Soul King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've fought enough already.\NAre you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still trying to get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why do you wanna get up, Soul King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the stone, Soul King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of getting Sanji back,\Nyou want a copy of the stone so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0} is a kind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I figured he'd never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of \Ntrap you set for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he's extremely kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so once he's determined to sacrifice himself\Nfor someone else, he'll stick to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, our captain\Nbelieves in himself and goes his own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:17:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to those two young men to decide\Nwhat's for the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you came for the stone\Nbecause you have nothing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if worse comes to worst\Nand Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0} decided not to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to blame himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell him there was a great payoff\Nfrom this rescue mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I must get it! The Road Ponegliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think your idea of "worst" is too light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji not returning is\Nthe worst thing that could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think no one's gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe all of you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fool regards his own death\Nas part of a plan, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:07.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,MIRRO-WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St... St... Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Tickle, tickle, tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot's special tickle, tickle, tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop tickling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say it! If you don't,\Nshe'll tickle you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it! I'll say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Carrot, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer our question.\NWhich mirror leads to the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember which mirror leads to where!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean you gotta ask the mirrors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ask?\N--The mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Mirrors know \Nwhat they're reflecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror, mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you is a mirror to the castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's me.\N--Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They answered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here! Me too!\N--Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mirror in Galette-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a hand mirror in a guest room\Non the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mirror in the ladies' room\Non the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do any of you reflect Luffy or Nami\Nor Brook or Pedro or Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who?\N--What do they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}sama{\i0} passed by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. They don't know how they look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me, Chobro!\NI'm good at drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:09.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,PRISON LIBRARY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:17.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, stop it, Luffy!\NYou're scaring me! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Your arms are \Ngonna really be torn apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!\NI gotta tell Sanji about Pudding's true colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I said don't do it! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... A little more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so reckless-{\i1}fa{\i0}.\NHey, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm busy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama told me to get Lola's whereabouts \Nout of you during the night-{\i1}fa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just say it now-{\i1}fa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not gonna betray my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna torture you-{\i1}fa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't say that so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna shoot you with a bowgun\Nonce every five seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so spill it whenever you feel like it-{\i1}fa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll kill me! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just come clean-{\i1}fa{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you, Warty-head!\NI'm not gonna let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be okay, Nami!\NI'll break my arms in five seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Whoa-whoa! I thought you weren't \Nallowed to enter the castle now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are fights everywhere.\NDon't be so hardheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:22:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Thousand Brick...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Why don't you sleep for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you got caught.\NI'm glad that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, do you want to get out of there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:12.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The shame of the family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what Sanji used to be called
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:18.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was a loving parent's \Nselfless affection behind it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:22.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His mother Sora's Struggle. And her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.27,0:23:26.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiju shares the secret behind the \Nbirth of the kindhearted Sanji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Sora's Wish! Germa's Failure - Sanji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
